": [], "activities": {}, "identifier": "stabilize", "method": "spell", "prepared": 0}}, {"name": "Static Circle", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>You extend your arms outward, emitting short streams of electrostatic energy. Each creature of your choice within 5 feet of you must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or take 1d6 lightning damage.\nThis power\u2019s power increases by 1d6 when you reach 5th level (2d6), 11th level (3d6), and 17th level (4d6).</p>", "chat": ""}, "source": {"custom": "", "book": "Esper Genesis Core Manual", "page": "", "license": "", "rules": "2014", "revision": 1}, "activation": {"type": "action", "value": 1, "condition": ""}, "duration": {"value": "", "units": "spec"}, "target": {"affects": {"type": "", "count": "", "choice": false}, "template": {"size": "", "units": "ft", "type": "", "contiguous": false}}, "range": {"value": "", "units": "self"}, "uses": {"max": "", "recovery": [], "spent": 0}, "level": 0, "school": "evo", "materials": {"value": "", "consumed": false, "cost": 0, "supply": 0}, "properties": [], "activities": {}, "identifier": "static-circle", "method": "spell", "prepared": 0}}, {"name": "Tricky Fingers", "type": "spell", "img": "icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>You are able to generate a minor telekinetic effect at any point within range. For the duration of the talent, you can use your action to generate kinetic energy with a minor hand motion. You can command this energy to manipulate an object, open an unlocked door or container, pick up an item, pull a switch or lever, or pour the contents out of a jar. \nYou can only generate one effect at a time which will last only for the duration. You may not use this energy to attack, activate weapons or complex triggers, or carry more than 10 pounds.</p>", "chat": ""}, "source": {"custom": "", "book": "Esper 